| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).answer, trunc(vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer)._score,Int64(3))                                                        |
|               |   Sort: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer)._score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=4                                                                                     |
|               |     Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).answer, trunc(vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer)._score, Int64(3)), vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer)._score |
|               |       TableScan: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer) projection=[_score, answer, id]                                                                                                                                          |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, answer@1 as answer, trunc(vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer)._score,Int64(3))@2 as trunc(vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer)._score,Int64(3))]                                       |
|               |   SortPreservingMergeExec: [_score@3 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], fetch=4                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[_score@3 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, answer@2 as answer, trunc(_score@1, 3) as trunc(vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer)._score,Int64(3)), _score@1 as _score]                                                             |
|               |         AggregateExec: mode=FinalPartitioned, gby=[id@0 as id], aggr=[_score, answer]                                                                                                                                               |
|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([id@0], 3), input_partitions=3                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[id@0 as id], aggr=[_score, answer]                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |               ProjectionExec: expr=[union_extract(json_get(key@1, id), int) as id, _spice.search_field@0 as _spice.search_field, 1 - distance@2 as _score]                                                                          |
